    "explanation": "<p>Let C.P. be Rs. <i class=\"ga-var\">x</i> and S.P. be Rs. <i class=\"ga-var\">y</i>. </p>\n<p>Then, 3(<i class=\"ga-var\">y</i> - <i class=\"ga-var\">x</i>) = (2<i class=\"ga-var\">y</i> - <i class=\"ga-var\">x</i>) &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://www.indiabix.com/_files/images/aptitude/1-sym-imp.gif\">  <i class=\"ga-var\">y</i> = 2<i class=\"ga-var\">x</i>.</p>\n<p>Profit = Rs. (<i class=\"ga-var\">y</i> - <i class=\"ga-var\">x</i>) = Rs. (2<i class=\"ga-var\">x</i> - <i class=\"ga-var\">x</i>) = Rs. <i class=\"ga-var\">x</i>.</p>\n<p>\n</p><table class=\"ga-tbl-answer\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n <tbody><tr class=\"ga-tr-divident\" align=\"center\">\n    <td class=\"ga-td-line-rpad\" rowspan=\"2\"><img src=\"https://www.indiabix.com/_files/images/aptitude/1-sym-tfr.gif\"> Profit % =</td>\n    <td class=\"ga-td-line\" rowspan=\"2\"><img src=\"https://www.indiabix.com/_files/images/aptitude/1-sym-oparen-h1.gif\"></td>\n    <td class=\"ga-td-divident\"><i class=\"ga-var\">x</i></td>\n    <td class=\"ga-td-line-lpad\" rowspan=\"2\">x 100</td>\n    <td class=\"ga-td-line\" rowspan=\"2\"><img src=\"https://www.indiabix.com/_files/images/aptitude/1-sym-cparen-h1.gif\">% = 100%</td>\n </tr>\n <tr class=\"ga-tr-divisor\" align=\"center\">\n    <td class=\"ga-td-divisor\"><i class=\"ga-var\">x</i></td>\n </tr> \n</tbody></table>\n<p></p>\n\n<p class=\"mx-bold mx-green\">Video Explanation: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/dPzF10mGsWE\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dPzF10mGsWE</a></p>",
